title: War of the Roses: She Sent the Nudes Back to Him
description: Emily thinks her boyfriend is cheating because she recently found nudes on his phone but he used the "crazy ex" excuse and that it's nothing. But then, Emily got a message from the ex that is very telling if it's true so she wants to find out for sure if he's cheating.
